# Input

```svelte
{#if answer === 42}
	<p>what was the question?</p>
	{#if answer === 42}
  	<p>what was the question?</p>
  	{#if answer === 42}
    	<p>what was the question?</p>
    {/if}
  {/if}
{/if}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#if answer === 42}
	<p>what was the question?</p>
	{#if answer === 42}
		<p>what was the question?</p>
		{#if answer === 42}
			<p>what was the question?</p>
		{/if}
	{/if}
{/if}

```
